              "free_text": [
                " Because of the large uncertainties associated",
                " with the neutron efficiency correction, the author",
                " does not wish to issue numerical data. The graph in",
                " NEANDC(E)-194 should be considered only as a",
                " qualitative illustration of the cross section",
                " excitation function."
              ]
